  "root_text": {
    "iti63:0.1": "Itivuttaka 63 ",
    "iti63:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti63:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti63:0.4": "Addhāsutta ",
    "iti63:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti63:2.1": "“Tayome, bhikkhave, addhā. ",
    "iti63:2.2": "Katame tayo? ",
    "iti63:2.3": "Atīto addhā, anāgato addhā, paccuppanno addhā—",
    "iti63:2.4": "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo addhā”ti. ",
    "iti63:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti63:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti63:3.1": "“Akkheyyasaññino sattā, ",
    "iti63:3.2": "akkheyyasmiṁ patiṭṭhitā; ",
    "iti63:3.3": "Akkheyyaṁ apariññāya, ",
    "iti63:3.4": "yogamāyanti maccuno. ",
    "iti63:4.1": "Akkheyyañca pariññāya, ",
    "iti63:4.2": "akkhātāraṁ na maññati; ",
    "iti63:4.3": "Phuṭṭho vimokkho manasā, ",
    "iti63:4.4": "santipadamanuttaraṁ. ",
    "iti63:5.1": "Sa ve akkheyyasampanno, ",
    "iti63:5.2": "santo santipade rato; ",
    "iti63:5.3": "Saṅkhāya sevī dhammaṭṭho, ",
    "iti63:5.4": "saṅkhyaṁ nopeti vedagū”ti. ",
    "iti63:6.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti63:6.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti63:0.1": "So It Was Said 63 ",
    "iti63:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti63:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti63:0.4": "Periods ",
    "iti63:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti63:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three periods. ",
    "iti63:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti63:2.3": "Past, future, and present. ",
    "iti63:2.4": "These are the three periods.” ",
    "iti63:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti63:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti63:3.1": "“Sentient beings who perceive the communicable, ",
    "iti63:3.2": "become established in the communicable. ",
    "iti63:3.3": "Not understanding the communicable, ",
    "iti63:3.4": "they fall under the yoke of Death. ",
    "iti63:4.1": "But having fully understood the communicable, ",
    "iti63:4.2": "they don’t conceive a communicator, ",
    "iti63:4.3": "as they’ve touched liberation with their mind, ",
    "iti63:4.4": "the supreme state of peace. ",
    "iti63:5.1": "Accomplished in the communicable, ",
    "iti63:5.2": "peaceful, in love with the state of peace; ",
    "iti63:5.3": "making use after reflection, firm in principle, ",
    "iti63:5.4": "a knowledge master cannot be reckoned.” ",
    "iti63:6.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti63:5.1": "Sa ve → sace (mr) "
  },
